The amount of os time ticks this task has been running






t_ctx_sw_cnt


The number of times that this task has been run






t_os_task_list


List pointer for global task list. All tasks are placed on this list






t_os_list


List pointer used by either the active task list or the sleeping task list






t_obj_list


List pointer for tasks waiting on a semaphore or mutex










